# Dockerfile-specific build context for deploy/coolify/hub/Dockerfile.
#
# This prevents the remote-hub image build from sending local artifacts such as
# release_reports/, diagnostics_output/, tools/, runtime/, revision_control/,
# .proto-dev/, debug_assets/, and other generated directories to Docker/Coolify.
#
# The hub image only needs the Python package and packaging metadata.

*
!pyproject.toml
!README.md
!main_computer/
!main_computer/**
